column2: SELECT   gal.objID,z.synthG as mag_#,z.synthR as mag_#,z.synthI as mag_#,   z.kcorrU as kcor_z0#_u,z.kcorrG as kcor_z0#_g,z.kcorrR as kcor_z0#_r,z.kcorrI as kcor_z0#_i,z.kcorrZ as kcor_z0#_z,   z.kcorrU0# as kcor_z0#_u,z.kcorrG0# as kcor_z0#_g,z.kcorrR0# as kcor_z0#_r,z.kcorrI0# as kcor_z0#_i,z.kcorrZ0# as kcor_z0#_z,   gal.petroRad_u,gal.petroRad_g,gal.petroRad_r,gal.petroRad_i,gal.petroRad_z,   gal.petroRadErr_u,gal.petroRadErr_g,gal.petroRadErr_r,gal.petroRadErr_i,gal.petroRadErr_z into mydb.Mag1#_#s_# FROM Galaxy as gal   JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestObjID=gal.objID and s.specObjID=gal.specObjID   JOIN PhotoZ as z ON z.objID=gal.objID WHERE   gal.ra BETWEEN # and #   AND gal.dec BETWEEN # and #   AND gal.petroRad_u># and gal.petroRad_g># and gal.petroRad_r># and gal.petroRad_i># and gal.petroRad_z># and gal.petroRadErr_g>#   AND gal.petroMag_g BETWEEN # and #   AND s.z<=#   AND (s.sourceType=&&& OR s.sourceType=&&&) ORDER BY   gal.objID
